1
00:00:12,479 --> 00:00:14,880
Uncle Yi, I want an ultraman.

2
00:00:14,881 --> 00:00:16,248
But I want the lemon flavor.

3
00:00:16,249 --> 00:00:17,977
Sure.

4
00:00:20,754 --> 00:00:23,051
That's all right.

5
00:00:39,339 --> 00:00:41,040
Keung, where are you?

6
00:00:41,041 --> 00:00:43,168
Thank you, Uncle Yi.

7
00:00:55,221 --> 00:00:57,484
It's over done!

8
00:01:14,607 --> 00:01:16,665
Leung.

9
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:22,114
Chief, what's the matter?

10
00:01:22,115 --> 00:01:24,883
See? The pork is over done.
I told you many times.

11
00:01:24,884 --> 00:01:27,653
Pork is the star of this dish.

12
00:01:27,654 --> 00:01:31,423
I... I just went to toilet
for a while, so...

13
00:01:31,424 --> 00:01:33,092
It's ridiculous!

14
00:01:33,093 --> 00:01:37,359
You're not in the mood all the day,
see? You caused trouble at last.

15
00:01:38,665 --> 00:01:40,632
What's the matter with you?

16
00:01:40,633 --> 00:01:43,936
There is only half hour
to the banquet.

17
00:01:43,937 --> 00:01:46,538
Now, the pork is over done.

18
00:01:46,539 --> 00:01:49,908
Can we serve without pork
in the pot?

19
00:01:49,909 --> 00:01:52,741
What we can do now
is to use the ''Blade''.

20
00:02:06,459 --> 00:02:08,517
Leung, borrow the Blade.

21
00:02:10,730 --> 00:02:13,432
The 5th descendant of the
Dragon Head Blade, Wong Bing-Yi,

22
00:02:13,433 --> 00:02:15,067
I'd like to borrow the Blade now.

23
00:02:15,068 --> 00:02:18,560
With the unification of the blade,
we'll do it righteous and filial.

24
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:33,152
Ah Yi borrows the Blade.

25
00:02:33,153 --> 00:02:34,119
What is it about?

26
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:37,088
The Chief is holding the
Dragon Head's Blade.

27
00:02:37,690 --> 00:02:39,091
What is it for?

28
00:02:39,092 --> 00:02:42,390
Why did he take out the Blade?

29
00:02:47,133 --> 00:02:48,700
This is my first time to view it.

30
00:02:48,701 --> 00:02:52,068
Wah, this is my first time
to view this Blade.

31
00:02:52,906 --> 00:02:56,466
Don't block my way;
I want to see how wonderful it is.

32
00:03:20,633 --> 00:03:21,633
Bravo!

33
00:03:21,634 --> 00:03:24,236
Woo, it's really wonderful!

34
00:03:24,237 --> 00:03:25,971
Second-Uncle,
you can tell the guests that...

35
00:03:25,972 --> 00:03:27,573
The banquet will be on time.

36
00:03:27,574 --> 00:03:30,409
So, I'll count on you
to make us some tasty pork.

37
00:03:30,410 --> 00:03:31,210
Sure, no problem.

38
00:03:31,211 --> 00:03:34,112
This is a red pocket for you,
for working smooth.

39
00:03:34,113 --> 00:03:34,980
Thank you, Uncle.

40
00:03:34,981 --> 00:03:36,815
Okay, the banquet
will be started on time.

41
00:03:36,816 --> 00:03:38,617
Come on, help me to serve.

42
00:03:38,618 --> 00:03:43,388
Little sis, 5th-Uncle...

43
00:03:43,389 --> 00:03:46,258
We wish you happy birthday!
Thank you.

44
00:03:46,259 --> 00:03:47,960
We wish you happy birthday!

45
00:03:47,961 --> 00:03:48,760
Good! Thank you for coming.

46
00:03:48,761 --> 00:03:49,595
Thank you, Uncle.

47
00:03:49,596 --> 00:03:50,796
Come on, cheers...

48
00:03:50,797 --> 00:03:53,031
Cheers!

49
00:03:53,032 --> 00:03:55,500
What a smell!

50
00:03:59,005 --> 00:04:01,132
It smells so good!

51
00:04:02,308 --> 00:04:03,208
Give me the salt.

52
00:04:03,209 --> 00:04:05,267
Here it is.

53
00:04:17,223 --> 00:04:19,281
It's done!

54
00:04:23,162 --> 00:04:24,896
Eat more! Come on, enjoy your food.

55
00:04:24,897 --> 00:04:27,065
Come on,

56
00:04:27,066 --> 00:04:29,261
come...

57
00:04:29,736 --> 00:04:31,803
Take it to that table,
and that table, too.

58
00:04:31,804 --> 00:04:33,972
Eat more! Come on...

59
00:04:33,973 --> 00:04:35,173
Eat more.

60
00:04:35,174 --> 00:04:36,936
Cheers!

61
00:04:38,778 --> 00:04:42,614
If Master Joe was here,
we wouldn't have been that messy.

62
00:04:42,615 --> 00:04:46,118
Even he is willing to help,
I won't let him do it.

63
00:04:46,119 --> 00:04:49,688
I promised my brother
to let his son achieve great success.

64
00:04:49,689 --> 00:04:52,487
But he is still a cook out there.

65
00:04:52,692 --> 00:04:54,459
Tidy up now.

66
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:57,588
Chief, oh no! What a trouble!

67
00:05:31,030 --> 00:05:33,293
Why did you do that?

68
00:05:45,211 --> 00:05:45,911
Don't let him go!

69
00:05:45,912 --> 00:05:48,113
He is the cook!
He intended to poison us!

70
00:05:48,114 --> 00:05:49,214
He should not be the Chief
of our village.

71
00:05:49,215 --> 00:05:51,580
Dare you want to go?

72
00:06:46,272 --> 00:06:48,831
Who asked you to do so?

73
00:06:49,776 --> 00:06:52,267
It's Master Joe.

74
00:07:02,488 --> 00:07:05,223
Wong Bing-Yi,
since you borrowed the Blade,

75
00:07:05,224 --> 00:07:07,092
You must be responsible.

76
00:07:07,093 --> 00:07:10,687
Wong, you are not qualified
to be a cook.

77
00:07:14,567 --> 00:07:16,201
I was being set up!

78
00:07:16,202 --> 00:07:17,335
Did I misunderstand you?

79
00:07:17,336 --> 00:07:19,738
You cooked the pork.

80
00:07:19,739 --> 00:07:23,208
Yi, you don't deserve
to have the Blade.

81
00:07:23,209 --> 00:07:24,676
Master Joe is the man behind...

82
00:07:24,677 --> 00:07:27,813
I decided to expel Wong Bing-Yi.

83
00:07:27,814 --> 00:07:31,647
Wong Kai-Joe will substitute him
for a while.

84
00:08:09,288 --> 00:08:13,918
KUNG FU CHEFS

85
00:08:15,895 --> 00:08:19,296
Tai-tung Martial Arts

86
00:08:48,461 --> 00:08:52,664
Students, before your graduation,

87
00:08:52,665 --> 00:08:56,368
Let's see who can put the emblem
of the school...

88
00:08:56,369 --> 00:08:58,770
Back to its original place.

89
00:08:58,771 --> 00:09:01,039
The one who can do it will be...

90
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,337
The first honored graduate
of the school.

91
00:09:05,278 --> 00:09:07,336
On your mark...

92
00:09:09,982 --> 00:09:11,949
Get set...

93
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,882
Go!

94
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:12,177
It is with him!

95
00:10:12,178 --> 00:10:14,339
Go after him!

96
00:10:19,885 --> 00:10:22,285
Don't let him go!

97
00:10:23,556 --> 00:10:24,990
Give it to me.

98
00:10:24,991 --> 00:10:26,725
Are you kidding me?

99
00:10:26,726 --> 00:10:29,057
It is with the principal.

100
00:10:29,462 --> 00:10:32,364
Don't come to me...

101
00:10:32,365 --> 00:10:34,566
Respect your principal!

102
00:10:34,567 --> 00:10:36,034
Who wants to be
the first honored graduate?

103
00:10:36,035 --> 00:10:38,298
Move!

104
00:10:38,871 --> 00:10:40,238
Are you serious?

105
00:10:40,239 --> 00:10:43,867
I wanna be!
Me too...

106
00:10:53,319 --> 00:10:56,321
I don't have it,

107
00:10:56,322 --> 00:10:58,089
it's not with me...

108
00:10:58,090 --> 00:11:00,091
I passed it to Ken'ichi.

109
00:11:00,092 --> 00:11:02,583
It is with Ken'ichi.

110
00:11:03,295 --> 00:11:05,030
Where is it? Where is it?

111
00:11:05,031 --> 00:11:06,064
Principal, who did you give it to?

112
00:11:06,065 --> 00:11:08,233
I... I gave it to that jerk!

113
00:11:08,234 --> 00:11:10,268
Where is he now?

114
00:11:10,269 --> 00:11:12,896
You bastard!

115
00:11:18,878 --> 00:11:21,938
Pal, thank you.

116
00:11:37,063 --> 00:11:40,065
Has Ken'ichi left?

117
00:11:40,066 --> 00:11:41,566
I am asking you.

118
00:11:41,567 --> 00:11:45,070
Has Ken'ichi left?

119
00:11:45,071 --> 00:11:47,672
I think he has just left,
maybe, perhaps,

120
00:11:47,673 --> 00:11:49,731
I think so...

121
00:11:49,809 --> 00:11:51,976
It's nonsense to ask you.

122
00:11:51,977 --> 00:11:54,012
I'll go after him.

123
00:11:54,013 --> 00:11:55,580
You don't need to.

124
00:11:55,581 --> 00:11:59,141
He asked me to give you this box
before he left.

125
00:12:16,969 --> 00:12:20,199
How dare he fool the principal!

126
00:12:42,294 --> 00:12:44,091
Watch out, it's breaking!

127
00:12:50,236 --> 00:12:52,260
It's school property.

128
00:13:17,096 --> 00:13:19,864
Principal, I have to leave now.

129
00:13:19,865 --> 00:13:22,500
Politeness, justice, honesty and
honor, patience and self control.

130
00:13:22,501 --> 00:13:24,335
I will never forget
what you have taught me.

131
00:13:24,336 --> 00:13:25,970
I made you these noodles.

132
00:13:25,971 --> 00:13:30,032
This is just a token from me.

133
00:13:32,478 --> 00:13:35,747
It's very kind of you.

134
00:13:35,748 --> 00:13:37,977
Rise.

135
00:13:39,351 --> 00:13:40,919
After leaving the school,

136
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:44,155
go to this place to look for
master Sum Wai-tak.

137
00:13:44,156 --> 00:13:45,723
What for?

138
00:13:45,724 --> 00:13:49,661
From this great master,
you can learn what you're lacking for.

139
00:13:49,662 --> 00:13:52,831
The principles of gourmandism are:
color, smell, taste, conception and appearance.

140
00:13:52,832 --> 00:13:55,099
Ken has cooking talent.

141
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,901
But he doesn't know much
about the idea of food.

142
00:13:56,902 --> 00:13:58,970
However, we cannot teach
the conception of food.

143
00:13:58,971 --> 00:14:01,973
He must figure it out in his life.

144
00:14:01,974 --> 00:14:04,876
If he can match himself with food,
then, he can make it.

145
00:14:04,877 --> 00:14:07,712
Although Ken isn't a local student,

146
00:14:07,713 --> 00:14:11,282
He has strong passion
on Chinese cookery.

147
00:14:11,283 --> 00:14:13,618
After some time, I am sure...

148
00:14:13,619 --> 00:14:15,780
He can become a great cook.

149
00:14:50,723 --> 00:14:53,987
Sis, do you think the smell of tea
can distract me?

150
00:14:55,461 --> 00:14:57,394
Please wait!

151
00:15:01,667 --> 00:15:04,035
Forget it, Ching,

152
00:15:04,036 --> 00:15:07,266
I am sure you can't get it
just by smelling.

153
00:15:07,706 --> 00:15:10,108
We should get ready
for servicing now.

154
00:15:10,109 --> 00:15:12,167
Come on, just say you can't make it.

155
00:15:13,479 --> 00:15:15,947
Kam-lui, I told you, remember?

156
00:15:15,948 --> 00:15:19,117
I want to serve our guests
nutritious soup,

157
00:15:19,118 --> 00:15:21,119
But not this kind of mixture.

158
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:23,110
You can smell it, can't you?

159
00:15:26,625 --> 00:15:29,327
This seems to be a nutritious soup,

160
00:15:29,328 --> 00:15:31,729
But actually,
it is medicine instead of soup.

161
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,598
Take it away.

162
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:35,700
I tried so much time
and effort for it.

163
00:15:35,701 --> 00:15:38,603
What a pity
that you still miss something.

164
00:15:38,604 --> 00:15:39,938
I have already helped you.

165
00:15:39,939 --> 00:15:42,134
But my sister is really great!

166
00:15:44,777 --> 00:15:46,711
Kam-lui, what is this black stuff?

167
00:15:46,712 --> 00:15:49,480
It's disgusting!
Take it away please.

168
00:15:49,481 --> 00:15:51,539
Take it away!

169
00:15:59,558 --> 00:16:01,685
My sister is really great!

170
00:16:02,728 --> 00:16:05,697
Have the goods
we ordered been delivered?

171
00:16:05,698 --> 00:16:07,893
I am now going to check it.

172
00:16:26,986 --> 00:16:28,186
What's wrong with you?

173
00:16:28,187 --> 00:16:29,053
Come and give me a hand.

174
00:16:29,054 --> 00:16:30,646
All right.

175
00:16:31,557 --> 00:16:33,458
Let me help you.

176
00:16:33,459 --> 00:16:34,359
Thank you.

177
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,884
You're welcome.

178
00:16:39,565 --> 00:16:40,531
Are you kidding?

179
00:16:40,532 --> 00:16:42,000
You messed up everything!

180
00:16:42,001 --> 00:16:42,567
I am sorry...

181
00:16:42,568 --> 00:16:46,526
If any of it breaks,
I'll cut the bill, you got it?

182
00:16:50,709 --> 00:16:52,540
Come on.

183
00:16:55,381 --> 00:16:56,381
Oh my head...

184
00:16:56,382 --> 00:16:57,915
It hurts!

185
00:16:57,916 --> 00:17:00,218
What are you looking at?

186
00:17:00,219 --> 00:17:03,381
Move those stuffs inside, hurry up!

187
00:17:04,156 --> 00:17:04,889
No, I...

188
00:17:04,890 --> 00:17:07,625
I'll check the bill later,
but I must check the goods first

189
00:17:07,626 --> 00:17:09,861
If any breaks, I won't pay the bill.

190
00:17:09,862 --> 00:17:12,130
If one is rotten,
I'll deduct 2 dollars, and so on

191
00:17:12,131 --> 00:17:13,398
Move now!

192
00:17:13,399 --> 00:17:15,764
Hurry up!

193
00:17:15,968 --> 00:17:20,336
You too, move those
near the door way first.

194
00:17:51,770 --> 00:17:53,905
Excuse me, sir...

195
00:17:53,906 --> 00:17:57,909
Do you want to eat in?

196
00:17:57,910 --> 00:18:00,037
This way please.

197
00:18:01,413 --> 00:18:03,514
What did you say?

198
00:18:03,515 --> 00:18:05,316
I said...

199
00:18:05,317 --> 00:18:06,651
First, I am not a coolie.

200
00:18:06,652 --> 00:18:09,253
Second, I didn't mean to hurt you.

201
00:18:09,254 --> 00:18:12,223
Third, I came here for Master Sum.

202
00:18:12,224 --> 00:18:14,191
The forth thing is...

203
00:18:15,828 --> 00:18:16,994
I am really hungry.

204
00:18:16,995 --> 00:18:19,931
Why didn't you voice out?

205
00:18:19,932 --> 00:18:23,367
Did you give me a chance?

206
00:18:23,368 --> 00:18:27,338
I'll make you pay for
hurting my head later.

207
00:18:27,339 --> 00:18:28,172
Please wait for me
right here for a minute.

208
00:18:28,173 --> 00:18:29,273
Since our shop
has just been in service,

209
00:18:29,274 --> 00:18:31,476
If you don't mind,
please sit inside.

210
00:18:31,477 --> 00:18:33,239
It's all right.

211
00:18:46,458 --> 00:18:48,092
You want to see Master Sum?

212
00:18:48,093 --> 00:18:51,562
So, you must tell me
what ingredients are put inside the soup.

213
00:18:51,697 --> 00:18:53,664
Sis.

214
00:19:10,449 --> 00:19:12,416
Thank you.

215
00:19:16,822 --> 00:19:19,051
The water from 3 rivers.

216
00:19:20,425 --> 00:19:22,627
So, you are a gourmet!

217
00:19:22,628 --> 00:19:24,618
I just know something about food.

218
00:19:28,534 --> 00:19:32,236
Did you make this Pu-er tea
with old tangerine peel?

219
00:19:32,237 --> 00:19:34,805
How did you know it?

220
00:19:34,806 --> 00:19:37,808
Old orange peel is as precious
as old ginseng.

221
00:19:37,809 --> 00:19:41,279
To mix tangerine peel
with old Pu-er tea,

222
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:45,546
It is the best drink to quench thirst 
and helps good digestion.

223
00:19:46,485 --> 00:19:48,286
You know much about tea.

224
00:19:48,287 --> 00:19:51,656
However, our food is even better
than this tea.

225
00:19:51,657 --> 00:19:54,792
I am sure you have never
tried that before.

226
00:19:54,793 --> 00:19:56,894
What do you want to order, sir?

227
00:19:56,895 --> 00:19:59,230
What is the signature dish
of your restaurant?

228
00:19:59,231 --> 00:20:02,033
All are signature dishes,
you can order anything you'd like to eat.

229
00:20:02,034 --> 00:20:04,035
''Cabbage in clear water'' please.

230
00:20:04,036 --> 00:20:06,737
''Cabbage in Clear Water''?

231
00:20:06,738 --> 00:20:10,007
So, is it steamed or boiled?

232
00:20:10,008 --> 00:20:12,910
Mind your tongue!
That is the famous Szechwan dish.

233
00:20:12,911 --> 00:20:14,312
Although this is a
Cantonese restaurant,

234
00:20:14,313 --> 00:20:18,647
Since you order it,
we'll get it ready for you.

235
00:20:22,120 --> 00:20:24,188
Have you figured it out?

236
00:20:24,189 --> 00:20:29,026
Are you kidding me?
This tastes like medicine.

237
00:20:29,027 --> 00:20:32,830
But I know there is
something special inside.

238
00:20:32,831 --> 00:20:35,333
This is a soup with 3 snakes
and a turtle. So disgusting!

239
00:20:35,334 --> 00:20:37,768
I can't imagine that
you're really great!

240
00:20:37,769 --> 00:20:42,672
So, do you know how to make
''Cabbage in clear water''?

241
00:20:43,308 --> 00:20:44,508
I am a cook,

242
00:20:44,509 --> 00:20:48,479
Sure I know how to make
such simple dish.

243
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:50,709
One for me please.

244
00:20:53,151 --> 00:20:56,621
Master, why does he order
Szechwan food in a Cantonese restaurant?

245
00:20:56,622 --> 00:20:58,322
It's weird.

246
00:20:58,323 --> 00:21:00,324
I think this is a cook too.

247
00:21:00,325 --> 00:21:03,728
He wants to try me
with that special dish.

248
00:21:03,729 --> 00:21:07,062
Luckily I am not nobody.

249
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:25,082
Bro, there is just cabbage and soup,

250
00:21:25,083 --> 00:21:26,951
Why people view this
as the greatest dish of all?

251
00:21:26,952 --> 00:21:31,422
Yi, for we villagers,
cabbage has special meaning.

252
00:21:31,423 --> 00:21:33,391
It is like our family.

253
00:21:33,392 --> 00:21:35,459
Normally, we won't pay
special attention to it,

254
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:38,029
However, when we lose it,
we will miss it.

255
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:42,899
You'll understand the warmth
and love of it

256
00:21:48,740 --> 00:21:50,867
Check please.

257
00:21:52,611 --> 00:21:56,814
Sir, is there any problem
with our cabbage?

258
00:21:56,815 --> 00:21:58,516
Be frank...

259
00:21:58,517 --> 00:22:00,712
This is far beyond standard.

260
00:22:01,153 --> 00:22:03,888
I don't understand what you mean...

261
00:22:03,889 --> 00:22:06,223
The cabbage and chicken are not bad.

262
00:22:06,224 --> 00:22:08,959
But the process is wrong.

263
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:11,295
The cabbage you made here...

264
00:22:11,296 --> 00:22:14,398
Any cook can make it.

