00:39:37,508 --> 00:39:40,340
My brother got hurt
because of saving me.

535
00:39:41,278 --> 00:39:42,512
It hurts!

536
00:39:42,513 --> 00:39:45,382
My father can no longer be a cook,
all because of him.

537
00:39:45,383 --> 00:39:47,578
He left the village.

538
00:39:48,152 --> 00:39:49,352
Bro!

539
00:39:49,353 --> 00:39:52,088
Stop it, I have no face
to stay any longer.

540
00:39:52,089 --> 00:39:55,149
Please take care of Joe for me.

541
00:39:59,430 --> 00:40:04,768
I promised my brother to
take good care of Joe, God knows that...

542
00:40:04,769 --> 00:40:07,170
He forced by me
to leave the village.

543
00:40:07,171 --> 00:40:09,730
It's a revenge.

544
00:40:10,708 --> 00:40:13,733
How can he do this to you?

545
00:40:14,378 --> 00:40:16,446
Forget it.

546
00:40:16,447 --> 00:40:19,814
Let bygones be bygones.

547
00:40:20,251 --> 00:40:22,152
In fact, your brother...

548
00:40:22,153 --> 00:40:26,523
Won the championship of the
World's Best Chef for 2 consecutive years.

549
00:40:26,524 --> 00:40:29,959
He gained much fame for us.

550
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:33,156
My brother is really a genius.

551
00:40:38,035 --> 00:40:39,934
Wrong.

552
00:40:51,482 --> 00:40:53,506
Wrong!

553
00:40:55,553 --> 00:41:00,649
Wrong!

554
00:41:33,224 --> 00:41:38,328
Cutting skills is easy to learn
but it needs non stop practice.

555
00:41:38,329 --> 00:41:42,832
For common people,
they just need to cut sharp.

556
00:41:42,833 --> 00:41:44,901
If a cook has better skills,

557
00:41:44,902 --> 00:41:48,638
He can handle chopping, hitting,
mashing and slashing well.

558
00:41:48,639 --> 00:41:51,407
That's already good skills.

559
00:41:51,408 --> 00:41:53,977
But if he wants to be a good cook,

560
00:41:53,978 --> 00:41:58,615
Different ingredients need
different kinds of cutting skills.

561
00:41:58,616 --> 00:42:02,449
So, it'll take much time
for real practice.

562
00:42:17,968 --> 00:42:19,235
Is it really that bad?

563
00:42:19,236 --> 00:42:21,571
I did it purposely for you.

564
00:42:21,572 --> 00:42:23,506
Thank you.

565
00:42:23,507 --> 00:42:26,532
I worked for one whole day.

566
00:42:27,912 --> 00:42:29,777
I already said thank you.

567
00:42:30,748 --> 00:42:33,239
Don't be cocky!

568
00:44:13,884 --> 00:44:17,020
Other than being fresh,
to make great food,

569
00:44:17,021 --> 00:44:20,123
We need great sauce to mix with it.

570
00:44:20,124 --> 00:44:22,492
Saucing is the soul of a dish.

571
00:44:22,493 --> 00:44:24,260
But different people
have different taste.

572
00:44:24,261 --> 00:44:27,130
But you will get bored for eating
same good food everyday.

573
00:44:27,131 --> 00:44:29,999
So,
all good cook can make good sauce.

574
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,967
Try it.

575
00:44:44,615 --> 00:44:48,117
Ying, why the sauce you made...

576
00:44:48,118 --> 00:44:51,382
are of the same taste?

577
00:44:53,257 --> 00:44:54,123
I think so.

578
00:44:54,124 --> 00:44:56,148
Kam-lui.

579
00:45:02,366 --> 00:45:06,135
Actually it's easy to make sauce.

580
00:45:06,136 --> 00:45:08,805
You just need a little patience.

581
00:45:08,806 --> 00:45:10,973
And some interest.

582
00:45:10,974 --> 00:45:14,272
And some imagination.

583
00:45:15,012 --> 00:45:16,612
There are few kinds of taste,

584
00:45:16,613 --> 00:45:20,950
sweet, sour, bitter, hot and salty.

585
00:45:20,951 --> 00:45:23,319
Just keep on trying.

586
00:45:23,320 --> 00:45:27,190
Mix with different ingredients.

587
00:45:27,191 --> 00:45:31,752
Then find out the best choice
of the guests, that's all

588
00:45:34,932 --> 00:45:38,162
Is it tasty, Kam-lui?

589
00:45:38,435 --> 00:45:40,636
It is sweet and salty.

590
00:45:40,637 --> 00:45:43,806
But I can taste sweet and hot
at the same time, it's great!

591
00:45:43,807 --> 00:45:46,366
How did you make it?

592
00:45:47,978 --> 00:45:51,013
I haven't tried
such special sauce before.

593
00:45:51,014 --> 00:45:53,049
Kam-lui, let's use this sauce today.

594
00:45:53,050 --> 00:45:54,450
Keep it well in the kitchen.

595
00:45:54,451 --> 00:45:56,085
Be careful.

596
00:45:56,086 --> 00:45:58,611
Kam-lui, I'll go with you.

597
00:46:03,494 --> 00:46:06,019
Ying, what are you thinking?

598
00:46:07,297 --> 00:46:12,301
I am thinking of a way to
make some delicious bean cube pudding.

599
00:46:12,302 --> 00:46:14,036
You want to make bean cube pudding?

600
00:46:14,037 --> 00:46:16,305
Greet me Master,
then I'll teach you.

601
00:46:16,306 --> 00:46:18,875
But I want the most delicious one.

602
00:46:18,876 --> 00:46:19,675
No problem.

603
00:46:19,676 --> 00:46:22,474
Master!

604
00:46:23,380 --> 00:46:27,250
The ingredients for making
bean cube pudding is simple.

605
00:46:27,251 --> 00:46:31,120
Soy beans, water and some substance
for solidification.

606
00:46:31,121 --> 00:46:35,887
The proportion of soy beans
and water may differ.

607
00:46:39,696 --> 00:46:42,096
Today, I'll teach you frying.

608
00:46:51,008 --> 00:46:54,010
For fried eggs, we love it to be
smooth, soft and with good smell.

609
00:46:54,011 --> 00:46:55,178
But how to make it smooth?

610
00:46:55,179 --> 00:46:57,346
The key point is to let air
enter the eggs.

611
00:46:57,347 --> 00:46:59,115
Bubble it.

612
00:46:59,116 --> 00:47:01,250
This shares the same theory
of making spongy cakes.

613
00:47:01,251 --> 00:47:03,586
I'll show you.

614
00:47:03,587 --> 00:47:06,248
Then, you'll count on yourself.

615
00:47:17,067 --> 00:47:19,168
The key point is to control
the temperature of the oil.

616
00:47:19,169 --> 00:47:21,337
Just one word, don't use boiled oil.

617
00:47:21,338 --> 00:47:22,805
If so, the eggs will be over done.

618
00:47:22,806 --> 00:47:24,432
Come on.

619
00:47:45,462 --> 00:47:48,664
Master, it is not done yet.

620
00:47:48,665 --> 00:47:51,634
Yes, it is to use the remained heat
to make it all done.

621
00:47:51,635 --> 00:47:53,169
So, the eggs will be smooth.

622
00:47:53,170 --> 00:47:57,607
Other than skills of frying,

623
00:47:57,608 --> 00:47:59,175
You need to pay attention
to breaking the eggs.

624
00:47:59,176 --> 00:48:01,611
And, most important of all is
to control the heat.

625
00:48:01,612 --> 00:48:04,547
It is simple to talk,
but it is really difficult.

626
00:48:04,548 --> 00:48:08,117
This is named
''Wong Po thousand layers of egg''

627
00:48:08,118 --> 00:48:11,320
Fried egg is just a simple dish.

628
00:48:11,321 --> 00:48:13,584
But it is really
something interesting!

629
00:48:18,762 --> 00:48:23,596
More simple the dish is,
more difficulty to be handled.

630
00:48:27,237 --> 00:48:31,070
It's really hard to cook great dish.

631
00:48:32,175 --> 00:48:34,810
No. it is not hard to cook well

632
00:48:34,811 --> 00:48:37,211
It's really hard
to perform well in life.

633
00:48:50,460 --> 00:48:52,552
Move now.

634
00:48:56,600 --> 00:48:58,000
This is the home made sauce.

635
00:48:58,001 --> 00:48:59,302
It's tasty!

636
00:48:59,303 --> 00:49:01,037
This is newly made,
hope you all like it.

637
00:49:01,038 --> 00:49:02,505
Boss. I haven't eaten
so delicious chicken.

638
00:49:02,506 --> 00:49:04,473
What is it about?

639
00:49:09,279 --> 00:49:10,179
What is it?

640
00:49:10,180 --> 00:49:12,307
What is it?

641
00:49:15,519 --> 00:49:17,720
This is...

642
00:49:17,721 --> 00:49:20,089
Obviously, it is a nail.

643
00:49:20,090 --> 00:49:21,190
Nail?

644
00:49:21,191 --> 00:49:23,726
Can you get it? It is a nail.

645
00:49:23,727 --> 00:49:25,962
What is it? What nail
you're talking about?

646
00:49:25,963 --> 00:49:29,465
There are some nails in the pot,
it can kill.

647
00:49:29,466 --> 00:49:30,967
Oh no!

648
00:49:30,968 --> 00:49:32,468
Don't get nervous,
it's just a misunderstanding.

649
00:49:32,469 --> 00:49:34,303
Kam-lui.

650
00:49:34,304 --> 00:49:35,371
What's the matter?

651
00:49:35,372 --> 00:49:37,669
Take a look at yourself.

652
00:49:39,176 --> 00:49:40,509
It is so sharp!

653
00:49:40,510 --> 00:49:43,479
I don't mind nails,
but I want it cooked well.

654
00:49:43,480 --> 00:49:45,675
It's not steak, I don't want it raw.

655
00:49:50,921 --> 00:49:53,689
I don't eat half done nails.

656
00:49:53,690 --> 00:49:55,024
Do you want to kill me?

657
00:49:55,025 --> 00:49:57,049
What do you want?

658
00:49:58,128 --> 00:49:59,595
You've gone too far!

659
00:49:59,596 --> 00:50:02,431
If you want to mess up,
you must use better trick

660
00:50:02,432 --> 00:50:05,501
How can you add so many nails
into the pot at the same time

661
00:50:05,502 --> 00:50:07,670
On one would be so stupid to cook
like this. This is a set up.

662
00:50:07,671 --> 00:50:09,305
It's hard to say

663
00:50:09,306 --> 00:50:13,109
There was precedent from your chef.

664
00:50:13,110 --> 00:50:15,168
What did you say

665
00:50:21,718 --> 00:50:26,154
Wong Bing-Yi, this is the present
from Master Joe

666
00:50:28,792 --> 00:50:29,925
Don't worry.

667
00:50:29,926 --> 00:50:35,489
This is the pork done by Chef Tin,
no problem.

668
00:50:37,300 --> 00:50:39,665
You'd better watch out

669
00:50:44,508 --> 00:50:46,475
Why?

670
00:50:46,476 --> 00:50:48,739
What does that mean?

671
00:51:09,266 --> 00:51:13,202
I can't imagine our business
would become this worse.

672
00:51:14,571 --> 00:51:16,368
Don't panic

673
00:51:17,808 --> 00:51:19,875
Why not?

674
00:51:19,876 --> 00:51:23,345
Now, we have no customers to come.

675
00:51:23,346 --> 00:51:27,509
If this goes on,
our restaurant will be closed.

676
00:51:28,452 --> 00:51:30,886
Who brought this bad luck to us,
huh?

677
00:51:37,127 --> 00:51:39,561
Brother Choi,
are you here for shopping?

678
00:51:42,599 --> 00:51:44,566
Let me handle it.

679
00:51:50,807 --> 00:51:54,435
We'd better not talk behind someone

680
00:51:57,080 --> 00:51:59,138
Don't mess up.

681
00:52:00,684 --> 00:52:05,382
I don't want to be bullied
but say nothing.

682
00:52:08,425 --> 00:52:09,959
Boss, how is it?

683
00:52:09,960 --> 00:52:11,722
How are you?

684
00:52:14,965 --> 00:52:17,666
Bitch! You're looking for trouble!

685
00:52:17,667 --> 00:52:18,400
What's up?

686
00:52:18,401 --> 00:52:20,095
Get lost!

687
00:52:21,037 --> 00:52:22,834
What's up?

688
00:52:22,906 --> 00:52:24,634
What are you doing?

689
00:52:29,513 --> 00:52:31,139
Stop!

690
00:53:43,019 --> 00:53:45,646
So? Be a hero?

691
00:53:52,762 --> 00:53:54,320
Go!

692
00:54:37,507 --> 00:54:38,407
What's up?

693
00:54:38,408 --> 00:54:40,136
Run!

694
00:54:49,452 --> 00:54:52,554
Stop!

695
00:54:52,555 --> 00:54:54,790
Freeze!

696
00:54:54,791 --> 00:54:55,557
Stay where you are!

697
00:54:55,558 --> 00:54:58,117
Freeze!

698
00:54:58,728 --> 00:55:01,492
Hurry up!

699
00:55:01,931 --> 00:55:02,865
Stop!

700
00:55:02,866 --> 00:55:04,856
Freeze!

701
00:55:05,101 --> 00:55:07,159
Stop!

702
00:55:26,489 --> 00:55:27,990
What do you want?

703
00:55:27,991 --> 00:55:30,015
No, thanks.

704
00:55:35,932 --> 00:55:38,832
Disgusting! Why did you stop me?

705
00:55:46,810 --> 00:55:50,302
Look, you have flour
all over your face.

706
00:56:04,060 --> 00:56:08,530
Come and join the 7th competition
for the ''Best Cook of China''.

707
00:56:08,531 --> 00:56:11,800
This campaign is held
once in 4 years, the winner...

708
00:56:11,801 --> 00:56:15,003
Will be awarded
the Best Cook of China,

709
00:56:15,004 --> 00:56:16,505
If we win...

710
00:56:16,506 --> 00:56:18,307
then we can save the reputation
of our restaurant.

711
00:56:18,308 --> 00:56:20,435
Let's hurry back to tell sister
about this.

712
00:56:39,362 --> 00:56:43,599
My dad is the best cook,
he is the best of the best.

713
00:56:43,600 --> 00:56:47,236
I can win the cup easily.

714
00:56:47,237 --> 00:56:50,831
No one can compete with me.

715
00:56:54,611 --> 00:56:56,942
I want a revenge.

716
00:57:05,688 --> 00:57:07,951
Hello...

717
00:57:08,992 --> 00:57:11,187
Okay, I'll wait for you.

718
00:57:13,196 --> 00:57:15,823
Sorry, I can't go.

719
00:57:18,968 --> 00:57:21,103
Yes, what's the matter?

720
00:57:21,104 --> 00:57:23,806
Master, please tell us.

721
00:57:23,807 --> 00:57:26,408
Sister and I take you as our family.

722
00:57:26,409 --> 00:57:29,139
We can help you!

723
00:57:30,113 --> 00:57:34,208
This matter bothers me
for a long time, I must settle it.

724
00:57:38,955 --> 00:57:41,056
Master, if you don't go,

725
00:57:41,057 --> 00:57:42,591
we won't go too.

726
00:57:42,592 --> 00:57:47,495
Ken, this is a
very important competition.

727
00:57:50,333 --> 00:57:52,634
What is more important
than the competition?

728
00:57:52,635 --> 00:57:54,369
Yes!

729
00:57:54,370 --> 00:57:57,206
It's you and this restaurant.

730
00:57:57,207 --> 00:58:00,008
I don't care the name
of being the best cook.

731
00:58:00,009 --> 00:58:03,579
For the restaurant,
you must try hard in the competition.

732
00:58:03,580 --> 00:58:07,015
Don't worry, we'll wait for you.

733
00:58:10,720 --> 00:58:12,915
Ken...

734
00:58:23,867 --> 00:58:26,392
Take this with you.

735
00:58:38,181 --> 00:58:41,350
Now, the competition for the
Best Chef of China begins.

736
00:58:41,351 --> 00:58:44,115
All the representatives are now
coming in the studio.

737
00:59:23,493 --> 00:59:25,790
Uncle Yu.

738
00:59:34,938 --> 00:59:37,172
This is a great event
for all great chefs in China.

739
00:59:37,173 --> 00:59:39,274
Ladies and gentlemen,
the 7th competition for the Best Chef of China...

740
00:59:39,275 --> 00:59:40,976
now begins!

741
00:59:40,977 --> 00:59:43,812
Let me introduce the judges.

742
00:59:43,813 --> 00:59:46,481
Mr. Yu Pun-cheong,
the chairman of the China Cookery Association.

743
00:59:46,482 --> 00:59:47,816
Mr. Liu Chi-wing, the famous chef.

744
00:59:47,817 --> 00:59:49,551
Ms Wong Lai-mui,
from the Catering Alliance.

745
00:59:49,552 --> 00:59:51,420
Mr. Wong Wing-chi, the chairman of the
Association For Catering Services Management.

746
00:59:51,421 --> 00:59:53,689
Mr. Yu Wing-man, the honorary
chairman of the Chef Association.

747
00:59:53,690 --> 00:59:55,691
Before the competition,

748
00:59:55,692 --> 00:59:57,526
We'd like to
invite the last champion,

749
00:59:57,527 --> 01:00:01,292
Master Tin Chou-dao from the King
of Cantonese Restaurant.

750
01:00:07,837 --> 01:00:10,168
Hi, Master Tin.

751
01:00:14,177 --> 01:00:16,577
Master.

752
01:00:20,049 --> 01:00:22,608
Is he still your master?

753
01:00:26,489 --> 01:00:28,684
Kam-lui.

754
01:00:29,926 --> 01:00:32,553
He is no longer your master.

755
01:00:33,796 --> 01:00:36,431
Fatty,

756
01:00:36,432 --> 01:00:38,300
I want to challenge you.

757
01:00:38,301 --> 01:00:41,536
Fine, where are you from?

758
01:00:41,537 --> 01:00:44,130
Sum's Restaurant.

759
01:00:45,208 --> 01:00:46,808
Now, I have to tell you the rules.

760
01:00:46,809 --> 01:00:48,477
This is a knockout.

761
01:00:48,478 --> 01:00:51,580
The judgment team will pick
2 teams among the 6.

762
01:00:51,581 --> 01:00:54,016
They will have the final race
in next time.

763
01:00:54,017 --> 01:00:55,584
Now, the theme is knife.

764
01:00:55,585 --> 01:00:59,087
In that case,
other than the outlook and taste,

765
01:00:59,088 --> 01:01:01,289
The chef must express
the skills of cutting.

766
01:01:01,290 --> 01:01:03,859
The cutting skill is a must
of a real chef.

767
01:01:03,860 --> 01:01:05,160
You'll have one hour
for competition.

768
01:01:05,161 --> 01:01:08,459
Now, I declare the race begins.

769
01:01:10,199 --> 01:01:12,223
I want to cook Szechwan's style
of Ox head.

770
01:01:14,804 --> 01:01:17,272
I understand what my master means.

771
01:01:17,273 --> 01:01:20,575
Kam-lui, we must win.

772
01:01:20,576 --> 01:01:22,177
Let's charge up.

773
01:01:22,178 --> 01:01:24,446
But what should we do?

774
01:01:24,447 --> 01:01:26,682
They are all picking ingredients.

775
01:01:26,683 --> 01:01:30,482
Sis, what should we do?

776
01:01:56,612 --> 01:01:57,846
Let's go
''The Four Stuffed Treasures''.

777
01:01:57,847 --> 01:02:00,076
The Four Stuffed Treasures''?

778
01:02:00,516 --> 01:02:02,584
It's more complicated than
''Eight Treasure Duck''.

779
01:02:02,585 --> 01:02:05,553
Don't you have confidence
in your cutting skills?

780
01:02:06,889 --> 01:02:08,156
I got it.

781
01:02:08,157 --> 01:02:12,527
I'll get the chicken, duck,
pigeon and the fillings.

782
01:02:12,528 --> 01:02:14,586
And quail too.

783
01:02:29,645 --> 01:02:34,809
Sis, what is Tin doing?

784
01:02:40,223 --> 01:02:43,525
This is the famous dish of Szechwan.

785
01:02:43,526 --> 01:02:46,756
It pays much attention in cutting.

786
01:03:08,718 --> 01:03:10,452
The competition is truly excited.

787
01:03:10,453 --> 01:03:12,387
Now, we have only...

788
01:03:12,388 --> 01:03:14,446
3 minutes left.

789
01:03:28,304 --> 01:03:30,505
Now, we have only...

790
01:03:30,506 --> 01:03:32,371
1 minute.

791
01:03:34,010 --> 01:03:35,841
5.

792
01:03:36,712 --> 01:03:38,736
4.

793
01:03:40,049 --> 01:03:41,948
3.

794
01:03:44,086 --> 01:03:45,917
2.

795
01:03:50,159 --> 01:03:52,092
Time's up.

796
01:03:55,631 --> 01:03:57,265
The 6 dishes are...

797
01:03:57,266 --> 01:04:00,168
Grapes and Fish from Wah Shun Hotel.

798
01:04:00,169 --> 01:04:02,571
Clams in chicken soup
from Chai-tai Restaurant.

799
01:04:02,572 --> 01:04:04,606
Golden Ox and Duck,
from Wan's Restaurant.

800
01:04:04,607 --> 01:04:06,374
Phoenix's tail and peach blossom
from Grandma's Restaurant.

801
01:04:06,375 --> 01:04:08,510
Four Stuffed Treasures
from Sum's Restaurant.

802
01:04:08,511 --> 01:04:10,412
Szechwan's Ox Head from the King
of Cantonese Restaurant.

803
01:04:10,413 --> 01:04:12,047
Judges,

804
01:04:12,048 --> 01:04:14,243
What a headache!

805
01:04:16,719 --> 01:04:19,554
The fish and the clams...

806
01:04:19,555 --> 01:04:22,123
The cutting skills and procedures
are all right.

807
01:04:22,124 --> 01:04:24,226
But they picked wrong ingredients.

808
01:04:24,227 --> 01:04:26,494
About the duck,

809
01:04:26,495 --> 01:04:30,398
It tastes well and spicy,
it looks good too.

810
01:04:30,399 --> 01:04:33,101
However, when it is peeled,

811
01:04:33,102 --> 01:04:35,904
the body of the duck was broken.

812
01:04:35,905 --> 01:04:39,174
And the dish from Grandma's
Restaurant, the prawns are fresh,

813
01:04:39,175 --> 01:04:41,209
The outlook is nice too.

814
01:04:41,210 --> 01:04:43,678
But the strong taste of wine..

815
01:04:43,679 --> 01:04:45,013
Just covers the taste of prawns.

816
01:04:45,014 --> 01:04:46,815
For the Four Stuffed Treasures,

817
01:04:46,816 --> 01:04:48,049
The cutting skills are excellent.

818
01:04:48,050 --> 01:04:51,820
The quail is in the pigeon,
then in the chicken,

819
01:04:51,821 --> 01:04:54,155
And finally inside the duck.

820
01:04:54,156 --> 01:04:56,358
It's a mixture of meat,
but with clear and layered taste.

821
01:04:56,359 --> 01:04:58,193
It's really wonderful.

822
01:04:58,194 --> 01:05:02,364
About the Ox Head,
it's really a master piece.

823
01:05:02,365 --> 01:05:04,266
It's a difficult task indeed.

824
01:05:04,267 --> 01:05:06,167
From the cutting skills
and the choice of ingredients,

825
01:05:06,168 --> 01:05:08,203
it's of the top level.

826
01:05:08,204 --> 01:05:09,971
Wonderful!
This ox-head is really wonderful.

827
01:05:09,972 --> 01:05:12,207
Now the judges
are having the final judgment.

828
01:05:12,208 --> 01:05:15,734
The 2 final teams
will be announced soon, they are...

829
01:05:20,683 --> 01:05:24,386
Ken from the Sum's Restaurant
and Tin from the King of Cantonese Restaurant.

830
01:05:24,387 --> 01:05:26,616
Congratulations!

831
01:05:27,723 --> 01:05:30,123
We have made it!

832
01:05:33,162 --> 01:05:35,357
We won!

833
01:05:37,967 --> 01:05:40,560
I wish Master was here with us.

834
01:05:48,811 --> 01:05:52,075
Master, we can enter the final race.

835
01:05:52,648 --> 01:05:54,683
But the other team is...

836
01:05:54,684 --> 01:05:56,879
The Sum's Restaurant.

837
01:05:58,487 --> 01:06:00,121
Master Joe, don't worry.

838
01:06:00,122 --> 01:06:02,487
I can figure it out.

839
01:06:10,466 --> 01:06:12,160
Let me go.

840
01:06:27,249 --> 01:06:29,341
Ken...

841
01:06:35,458 --> 01:06:38,483
Come and fight with me
if you're a man.

842
01:06:51,707 --> 01:06:55,267
Ken, watch out!

843
01:07:06,922 --> 01:07:08,753
Ken.

844
01:07:10,926 --> 01:07:13,628
Nice food can make people happy.

845
01:07:13,629 --> 01:07:15,797
But if the chef isn't happy,

846
01:07:15,798 --> 01:07:19,165
How can he pass happiness
to others through food

847
01:07:20,469 --> 01:07:22,037
When I see you going back
to the village,

848
01:07:22,038 --> 01:07:25,006
I can tell you
finally figured it out.

849
01:07:25,007 --> 01:07:27,031
Thank you.

850
01:07:29,311 --> 01:07:31,246
I must thank you indeed.

851
01:07:31,247 --> 01:07:33,214
If you didn't teach them
whole-heartedly,

852
01:07:33,215 --> 01:07:36,149
They can't enter the final race.

853
01:07:37,319 --> 01:07:41,255
It's all because they are talented.

854
01:08:22,531 --> 01:08:25,158
Ken, thank you.

855
01:08:26,535 --> 01:08:28,703
I am so sleepy...

856
01:08:28,704 --> 01:08:30,672
Are you?

857
01:08:30,673 --> 01:08:32,834
Don't sleep,

858
01:08:33,676 --> 01:08:38,044
I have many places to go with you.

859
01:08:40,449 --> 01:08:44,043
I have so many things to do with...

860
01:08:45,688 --> 01:08:49,214
Why happiness is so short?

861
01:08:56,031 --> 01:08:58,692
Because...

862
01:08:59,301 --> 01:09:04,465
People have many unhappy times.

863
01:09:18,888 --> 01:09:20,980
Ah Yi!

864
01:09:55,424 --> 01:09:57,619
You're something!

865
01:09:59,528 --> 01:10:01,518
Sit down.

866
01:10:07,536 --> 01:10:09,469
What do you want?

867
01:10:09,805 --> 01:10:12,774
Nothing, I just come to see you.

868
01:10:12,775 --> 01:10:15,140
Isn't it too late?

869
01:10:15,277 --> 01:10:17,011
Not late at all.

870
01:10:17,012 --> 01:10:21,744
If you are a bit late,
you will not see him.

871
01:10:22,685 --> 01:10:26,421
Cut the crap, you're not welcomed.

872
01:10:26,422 --> 01:10:29,290
I am your nephew,
I came specially to see you.

873
01:10:29,291 --> 01:10:31,192
Why don't you want to see me?

874
01:10:31,193 --> 01:10:35,094
I think I am not heartless.

875
01:10:35,331 --> 01:10:38,633
Uncle, your student
wounded my fellows.

876
01:10:38,634 --> 01:10:40,735
He should pay for it, right?

877
01:10:40,736 --> 01:10:44,728
You know pretty well
for what you did.

878
01:10:45,975 --> 01:10:48,636
What?

879
01:10:50,579 --> 01:10:55,850
You kicked my father away
for the Dragon Head's Blade.

880
01:10:55,851 --> 01:10:58,419
Now, you want to take my cup
for the Best Chef away?

881
01:10:58,420 --> 01:11:01,856
This should be what I told you.

882
01:11:01,857 --> 01:11:04,552
Your uncle did nothing wrong.

883
01:11:05,961 --> 01:11:08,229
Stop!

884
01:11:08,230 --> 01:11:09,664
No matter you believe it or not.

885
01:11:09,665 --> 01:11:11,866
Your father has his reason to leave.

886
01:11:11,867 --> 01:11:15,336
Okay, I have my reason to...

887
01:11:15,337 --> 01:11:18,067
Fix that bastard and the bitch.

888
01:11:28,417 --> 01:11:31,185
This is between us,
there is nothing to do with them.

889
01:11:31,186 --> 01:11:32,914
Yeah.

890
01:11:34,757 --> 01:11:36,724
I don't want to do anything to them.

891
01:11:36,725 --> 01:11:40,428
I just bring you some present.

892
01:11:40,429 --> 01:11:42,396
Leung.

893
01:11:42,665 --> 01:11:44,365
Master Joe, why not leave him alone?

894
01:11:44,366 --> 01:11:47,096
I don't want to repeat.

895
01:11:48,437 --> 01:11:52,974
Well, my fellows accidentally
locked up your student,

896
01:11:52,975 --> 01:11:56,778
And a young girl inside the freezer.

897
01:11:56,779 --> 01:12:01,045
And they accidentally
locked up the door.

898
01:12:02,418 --> 01:12:04,085
But don't worry.

899
01:12:04,086 --> 01:12:08,044
I've kept the key for you,
do you want it?

900
01:12:09,024 --> 01:12:11,992
I am sorry, I failed to hold it.

901
01:12:12,761 --> 01:12:15,923
The key is inside,
take it or leave it.

902
01:12:17,466 --> 01:12:21,424
You can take time to consider it,
but they just can't wait too long.

903
01:12:35,884 --> 01:12:38,375
I've got no choice.

904
01:12:40,155 --> 01:12:42,452
No!

905
01:12:42,758 --> 01:12:44,885
That key is not the true one.

906
01:12:46,161 --> 01:12:48,094
I've got the right one here.

907
01:12:55,404 --> 01:12:58,964
Come on, it's over

908
01:13:03,178 --> 01:13:05,543
Thank you.

909
01:13:06,682 --> 01:13:08,774
I must thank you indeed.

910
01:13:15,257 --> 01:13:18,693
Master Joe has lost control,
please take care.

911
01:13:18,694 --> 01:13:20,718
Take care.

912
01:13:49,958 --> 01:13:51,692
The next Best Chef
will be found soon.

913
01:13:51,693 --> 01:13:53,717
The theme of this final race is...

914
01:13:54,263 --> 01:13:55,363
Soup.

915
01:13:55,364 --> 01:13:57,265
The Chinese always need soup
in the banquet.

916
01:13:57,266 --> 01:13:58,966
Other than making soup,

917
01:13:58,967 --> 01:14:00,401
the participants must achieve
one more thing.

918
01:14:00,402 --> 01:14:02,069
That is...

919
01:14:02,070 --> 01:14:03,871
Purity.

920
01:14:03,872 --> 01:14:07,466
Sis, what does it mean?

921
01:14:07,709 --> 01:14:09,777
That means, no favour
is the best favour.

922
01:14:09,778 --> 01:14:13,381
So the cook cannot add seasoning
into the soup.

923
01:14:13,382 --> 01:14:15,149
In the arts of cookery,

924
01:14:15,150 --> 01:14:18,820
One way is to cook without seasoning,

925
01:14:18,821 --> 01:14:21,222
it is to let people eat the real
taste of the food.

926
01:14:21,223 --> 01:14:22,924
The best cooks of the Shang
and Chau Dynasty,

927
01:14:22,925 --> 01:14:24,992
They integrated the arts of cookery,

928
01:14:24,993 --> 01:14:27,728
With philosophy.

929
01:14:27,729 --> 01:14:29,397
That is ''Purity is the best''.

930
01:14:29,398 --> 01:14:30,865
I can't imagine

931
01:14:30,866 --> 01:14:35,002
you'd give up the competition
for that rusty blade.

932
01:14:35,003 --> 01:14:36,904
Do you like this blade?

933
01:14:36,905 --> 01:14:38,606
You really like to be Chief.

934
01:14:38,607 --> 01:14:40,174
Don't blame me of being heartless.

935
01:14:40,175 --> 01:14:43,075
I'll let you be the Chief
for one day.

936
01:14:43,846 --> 01:14:47,042
I now declare the beginning
of the competition.

937
01:14:50,252 --> 01:14:52,879
Ken, what soup should we make?

938
01:15:11,406 --> 01:15:16,434
Why these cabbages be viewed
as the best food?

939
01:15:17,112 --> 01:15:22,216
Cabbages mean a lot
to the villagers.

940
01:15:22,217 --> 01:15:24,852
They are like our family.

941
01:15:24,853 --> 01:15:27,088
Normally, you won't feel much.

942
01:15:27,089 --> 01:15:31,125
But when you lose it,
you'll feel how much you love it.

943
01:15:31,126 --> 01:15:33,856
You'll understand it in future.

944
01:15:36,265 --> 01:15:37,965
Kam-lui.

945
01:15:37,966 --> 01:15:40,263
Let's do ''Cabbage in Clear Water''.

946
01:15:40,869 --> 01:15:45,863
Master said, the fame of the
''Best Cook'' isn't important to him

947
01:15:47,676 --> 01:15:51,077
Except Sum's Restaurant!

948
01:15:53,515 --> 01:15:56,609
All right, let's do Cabbage
in Clear Water.

949
01:16:21,810 --> 01:16:25,541
Master Tin, how can you
get these ingredients...

950
01:16:26,114 --> 01:16:28,980
Preparation is always important
to achieve success.

951
01:16:30,719 --> 01:16:33,321
This dish is named with
''Clear Water'',

952
01:16:33,322 --> 01:16:37,349
it is because the soup is as
clear as water.

953
01:16:45,233 --> 01:16:48,669
The method is, mined the chicken,

954
01:16:48,670 --> 01:16:51,866
Then drop them evenly
inside the chicken soup.

955
01:16:55,911 --> 01:16:59,614
When it sinks,

956
01:16:59,615 --> 01:17:05,109
It'll absorb the remained fats
and other materials.

957
01:18:09,885 --> 01:18:12,683
Kam-lui, give me the cabbages.

958
01:18:14,690 --> 01:18:17,224
This is not normal cabbages.

959
01:18:17,225 --> 01:18:21,991
We must pick the heart
of the cabbages.

960
01:18:28,570 --> 01:18:32,606
Then, get some fine needles.

961
01:18:32,607 --> 01:18:36,941
Stab the needles into the leaves
to make numerous fine holds.

962
01:18:37,279 --> 01:18:40,646
But don't ruin the outlook
of the cabbages.

963
01:19:06,875 --> 01:19:09,043
Then, add the cooked soup...

964
01:19:09,044 --> 01:19:12,480
into the pot with cabbages.

965
01:19:12,481 --> 01:19:15,506
And then put it into the steamer
for steaming.

966
01:19:30,098 --> 01:19:32,395
What is it about?

967
01:19:34,369 --> 01:19:37,404
For traditional method,
only the bottom is heated.

968
01:19:37,405 --> 01:19:39,206
All the heat comes from the bottom.

969
01:19:39,207 --> 01:19:43,477
Now, he uses this device,

970
01:19:43,478 --> 01:19:46,674
So it will receive heat evenly
all over the pot.

971
01:21:33,121 --> 01:21:38,192
When it is opened, even the Buddha
is attracted to jump over the wall for it.

972
01:21:38,193 --> 01:21:41,195
''Buddha jumps the wall'',
it is absolutely the best soup of the world.

973
01:21:41,196 --> 01:21:45,325
''Cabbage in Clear Water''
is no match for it.

974
01:21:53,475 --> 01:21:55,567
Wait.

975
01:22:03,752 --> 01:22:07,688
Make it a signature dish
of Sum's Restaurant.

976
01:22:18,833 --> 01:22:23,463
Sis, that's my bean cube.

977
01:22:40,722 --> 01:22:42,712
Dragon Head's Blade.

978
01:23:08,183 --> 01:23:11,049
How come the bean cube disappeared?

979
01:23:24,499 --> 01:23:27,835
Why the Szechwan cook view this
as treasure?

980
01:23:27,836 --> 01:23:32,006
To make great food with some cheap
and common ingredients,

981
01:23:32,007 --> 01:23:34,608
It is the top level of cookery.

982
01:23:34,609 --> 01:23:37,978
And it implies the top level
of life performance.

983
01:23:37,979 --> 01:23:40,714
This is the real taste of food.

984
01:23:40,715 --> 01:23:43,843
Purity!

985
01:24:40,208 --> 01:24:41,375
The result is,

986
01:24:41,376 --> 01:24:45,903
Ken Lung from Sum's Restaurant
is the new Best Cook of China.

987
01:24:46,548 --> 01:24:50,575
Bravo! Wonderful!

988
01:24:59,727 --> 01:25:01,785
Brother.

989
01:25:03,031 --> 01:25:06,625
Since you have come,
why not have a sip?

990
01:25:31,359 --> 01:25:34,191
This is the taste of cabbage.

991
01:25:35,930 --> 01:25:38,332
Who is he?

992
01:25:38,333 --> 01:25:40,367
We haven't seen for ages,
how are you?

993
01:25:40,368 --> 01:25:42,165
I am fine.

994
01:25:42,804 --> 01:25:46,762
Master Wong, how are you doing?

995
01:25:48,676 --> 01:25:51,778
Is she Sam Ching?
Right.

996
01:25:51,779 --> 01:25:53,714
So you must be Sum Ying.

997
01:25:53,715 --> 01:25:57,050
Sis, is he...

998
01:25:57,051 --> 01:26:01,388
He is our father's student,
Master Wong Bing-kei.

999
01:26:01,389 --> 01:26:03,550
Dad...

1000
01:26:04,959 --> 01:26:07,794
Dad, please don't leave.

1001
01:26:07,795 --> 01:26:10,564
Dad...

1002
01:26:10,565 --> 01:26:12,633
Dad...

1003
01:26:12,634 --> 01:26:14,567
I did it wrong!

1004
01:26:16,371 --> 01:26:20,974
Ken, my brother and I think that
you're the best one to have this blade.

1005
01:26:20,975 --> 01:26:23,410
We hope you can make good food
with it.

1006
01:26:23,411 --> 01:26:26,175
To give happiness to the world!

1007
01:26:34,522 --> 01:26:36,890
I will leave tomorrow.

1008
01:26:36,891 --> 01:26:38,592
So soon.

1009
01:26:38,593 --> 01:26:40,027
This is my plan.

1010
01:26:40,028 --> 01:26:41,528
I have something for you.

1011
01:26:41,529 --> 01:26:42,829
It's made by me.

1012
01:26:42,830 --> 01:26:44,922
Sorry.

1013
01:26:54,876 --> 01:26:57,367
Don't be sad.

1014
01:27:00,715 --> 01:27:05,049
I've tried it.

1015
01:27:05,253 --> 01:27:08,187
What you made is best.

1016
01:27:10,191 --> 01:27:12,292
I don't know what sister
is thinking.

1017
01:27:12,293 --> 01:27:15,887
Why makes you learn cooking skills
from Wong?

1018
01:27:18,366 --> 01:27:21,935
Master is a great cook, it's really
your luck to learn cookery from him.

1019
01:27:21,936 --> 01:27:24,233
I don't care.

1020
01:27:25,373 --> 01:27:29,070
I'll leave this happiness to you!

1021
01:27:29,244 --> 01:27:30,244
No laughing.

1022
01:27:30,245 --> 01:27:33,614
Look at you! You're so handsome!

1023
01:27:33,615 --> 01:27:34,781
Really?

1024
01:27:34,782 --> 01:27:36,550
You have rosy cheeks!

1025
01:27:36,551 --> 01:27:38,385
I am sure you don't have
female students in school.

1026
01:27:38,386 --> 01:27:40,954
Haven't you been touched by women?

1027
01:27:40,955 --> 01:27:42,888
So what?

1028
01:27:44,759 --> 01:27:47,327
No matter you're not gentleman like.

1029
01:27:47,328 --> 01:27:49,763
And you are stupid!

1030
01:27:49,764 --> 01:27:52,132
You are so dull!

1031
01:27:52,133 --> 01:27:56,228
You don't understand girls at all!

1032
01:27:57,005 --> 01:27:58,805
But I can cook

1033
01:27:58,806 --> 01:28:01,171
No need to understand girls

